# Local SQLite dev database (Prisma's `prisma db push`/`prisma migrate dev`
# create these next to prisma/schema.prisma; SQLite also creates -journal
# and, in WAL mode, -wal/-shm sidecar files alongside the main .db file)
*.db
*.db-journal
*.db-wal
*.db-shm

